Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: botlib
Version: 13
Summary: Framework to program bots.
Home-page: https://bitbucket.org/bthate/botlib
Author: Bart Thate
Author-email: bthate@dds.nl
License: Public Domain
Description: 
        
        BOTLIB is a python3 framework to use if you want to program IRC or XMPP bots.
        
        Copyright (C) 2017 Bart Thate
        
        Permission to use, copy, modify, and/or distribute this software for any
        purpose with or without fee is hereby granted.
        
